name: 2014 Calendar Tea Towel
description:
Makes a cute hostess gift, and adds a touch of whimsy to any kitchen! Also makes a great reusable wrap for small gifts.

This towel is designed and hand sewn by Fat Bird Designs
Info:

• Printed digitally on linen-cotton Canvas, (55% linen/45% combed cotton).

• Includes corner loop in the upper right hand corner, so you can hang it up anywhere!

• Finished size: approximately 16-1/2" x 21", machine hemmed.

Care for your tea towel:
• Machine wash warm or cool on a gentle/delicate setting, using phosphate-free detergent. Line dry or tumble dry cool.

• Color may fade slightly after washing, and fabric will soften with every wash for a cute shabby chic tea towel!

• American Made!

Please allow 2 weeks processing before this item ships. Email us regarding rush orders *additional fees will apply. 

Thanks for shopping and supporting independent artists!

name: Hand Painted Hostess Apron Blue Bird
description:
NEW! NEW! NEW!

Hand Painted
100% Cotton 
100% Hand Made in the USA


This one of a kind apron includes a matching hand painted finger tip towel. Perfect for keeping your fingers and apron clean, because the hostess has to always look her best! Each apron is hand sewn out of high quality unbleached cotton which is super soft and absorbent. The ties are extra long so they can be tied in the front or back. The waistband has a towel loop to hold your figure tip towel in place. 

There will only be one of each design ever made so each apron is wearable art!  Machine washable!

*one size fits most*
